ibution or use would be contrary to local laws or regulations. Moneta Funded does not operate as a broker and does not provide brokerage or financial services. Funds paid to Moneta Funded do not constitute client money and are a subscription paid to Moneta Funded to participate in trading challenges. The technical infrastructure supporting the Moneta Funded platforms and market data is supplied through third-party liquidity providers.\n\nDisclaimer:\nIn compliance with global regulatory standards and our internal risk management policies, Moneta Funded does not onboard clients from Afghanistan, Thailand, Cuba, Myanmar, North Korea, UAE, Venezuela, Iran, and Vietnam.\n\nFor any enquiries, please contact support@monetafunded.com.\n\nWe use cookies to enhance your user experience, provide personalised content and analyse traffic. Cookie Policy.\n\nAccept All Decline All",
